        "content": "Hjornskar Head-Smasher is a Nord guard stationed in Dragonsreach — named for his preferred method of dealing with threats.",
        "display_name": "Hjornskar Head-Smasher - Dragonsreach Guard",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.55,
