        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWhiterunFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWhiterun\")",
        "content": "Lydia is a Nord warrior assigned as the Dragonborn's housecarl after acquiring Breezehome. A capable shield-maiden who follows the Dragonborn into danger without complaint.",
