        "content": "Kodlak Whitemane is the Harbinger of the Companions — first among equals at Jorrvaskr. Old, scarred, and respected. He carries the beast blood and would see his soul saved before his death.",
        "display_name": "Kodlak Whitemane - Harbinger of the Companions",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.9,
        "knowledge_key": "whiterun.people.kodlak",
