        "content": "Vilkas and Farkas are twin warriors of the Companions' Circle. Vilkas is sharp and bookish for a Nord; Farkas is the quieter of the two, with a slower wit but unmatched strength.",
        "display_name": "Vilkas and Farkas - Companions Twins",
